-*- coding: utf-8-unix -*-

			News file for CCStructs
			=======================

Revision 0.3.0-devel.3
----------------------

* Upgraded to CCExceptions version 0.10.0.

* Upgraded to CCMemory version 0.3.0.

* Upgraded to CCTests version 0.5.0.


Revision 0.3.0-devel.2
----------------------

* Added CSS file for HTML documentation.


Revision 0.3.0-devel.1
----------------------

* Fixed error in name generation for "ccname_init()" with 2 variants.


Revision 0.3.0-devel.0
----------------------

The release series 0.3 is backwards incompatible with the previous one.

* Upgraded dependency upon CCExceptions to version 0.9.0.

* Upgraded dependency upon CCTests to version 0.4.1.

* Upgraded dependency upon CCMemory to version 0.2.2.

* Adapted code to new API.

* Reimplemented dtor trait for better interface with CCExceptions.

* Added guarded constructors for "ccstructs_pathname_t".

* Added copy constructors for "ccstructs_pathname_t", plain and guarded.

* Renamed "interfaces" to "traits", which is a more appropriate name for
  the facilities.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.4
----------------------

* Updated packaging infrastructure.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.3
----------------------

* Updated packaging infrastructure.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.2
----------------------

* Added a variant to "ccname_init() and "ccname_new()".


Revision 0.2.0-devel.1
----------------------

* Package infrastructure development.

* Added support  for one  more variant specification  to "ccname_init()"
  and "ccname_new()".


Revision 0.2.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Development of build infrastructure.

* Renamed "dtors" interface to "dtor".

* Added experimental header file "ccnames.h".

* BACKWARDS  INCOMPATIBILITY The  code started  using the  facilities of
  "ccnames.h".

* BACKWARDS INCOMPATIBILITY Renamed the interface "ccstructs_writable_I"
  to "ccstructs_dumpable_I".

* BACKWARDS  INCOMPATIBILITY  Renamed  the  serialisation  interface  to
  "ccstructs_serialiser_I" and "ccstructs_deserialiser_I".


Revision 0.1.0-devel.2
----------------------

* Added macro "ccstructs_core()".

* Added "pathname" interface.

* BACKWARDS INCOMPATIBILITY Renamed some types from "_iface_" to "_I_".


Revision 0.1.0-devel.1
----------------------

* BACKWARDS INCOMPATIBILITY Rewritten the "writable" interface to not be
  tied to standard streams for output.


Revision 0.1.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Initial development release.


